Please see the other .readme files and website[1] for detailed
documentation.

pitrtools is a Python + PostgreSQL application that assists in the
provisioning of Hot Standby, Warm Standby, Cold Standby, Streaming
Replication clusters and multiple standbys (slaves). It supports all
PostgreSQL versions starting from 9.2.

Requirements:

 * Rsync
 * Python >= 2.6
 * SSH
 * PostgreSQL 9.2+

Website:

[1] https://public.commandprompt.com/projects/pitrtools/wiki
